00:02:49.879 --> 00:02:50.680
<v Speaker 1>Venir.

00:02:50.680 --> 00:02:52.120
<v Speaker 1>Venir, good.

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:53.480
<v Speaker 1>I come.

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:55.200
<v Speaker 1>Bengo.

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:56.000
<v Speaker 1>Bengo.

