<v Speaker 1>To put poner.

00:03:33.500 --> 00:03:34.060
<v Speaker 1>Poner.

00:03:34.060 --> 00:03:35.100
<v Speaker 1>And I put

00:03:36.500 --> 00:03:37.379
<v Speaker 1>Tongo.

00:03:37.379 --> 00:03:38.180
<v Speaker 1>Tongo.

00:03:38.180 --> 00:03:38.660
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:03:38.660 --> 00:03:46.420
<v Speaker 1>We have the sir, to say, or to tell, and we get ego, which is even more irregular, but we see the geo.

00:03:46.340 --> 00:03:54.660
<v Speaker 1>we have aser to make or to do and we get ago oir which means

00:03:54.960 --> 00:04:03.360
<v Speaker 1>to hear oir and we have oigo eye here traer traer means to bring

